snippet.title: Floor 0 (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Gameplay trailer for our upcoming release titled 'Floor0'

The game involves hunting for anomalies within the level. If the player manages to spot an anomaly, they retreat back to the elevator and progress further. If the player fails to spot an anomaly, their progress is halted.
